  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="3322374">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/3322374/" class="title-link">有点失望</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-3322374"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/24609869/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u24609869-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/24609869/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">Deddy</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-06-10"
      class="main-meta">2010-06-10 19:10:00</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_3322374_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  整体来说吧，史料不错，特别是奏折，看得出李督抚有相当的文字功底，所选奏折完全可以作为在公务员或国企系统工作的诸位的公文写作学习教材，只是分析稍显单薄，且比较拘泥于旧见，特别是对洋务运功以及相关人员的评价，仿佛在读中学历史课本，这点相当无趣。

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/3322374/#comments">(2回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">1有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_3322374_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_3322374_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
